title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Your definitions of whats beautiful and tasteful are likely to be challenged and broadened today. Even if you view yourself as the most cosmopolitan of your inner circle, you might encounter art or music that throws your ideas of attractiveness for a loop. You could surprise yourself by enjoying an unfamiliar museum, a new band, or even a particular food that you previously avoided. Your only obligation is to stay open and assume nothing while the mysterious Scorpio Moon tangos with sensual Venus in your 9th House of Expansion. Let discovery work its own magic. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
